@startuml
title JSON-RPC 模块交互序列 - Stdio 与 HTTP 双模式

skinparam sequenceArrowColor #546E7A
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #607D8B
skinparam participantBackgroundColor #E3F2FD
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam noteBorderColor #9E9E9E

participant "Stdio客户端" as SC #E8F5E9
participant "StdioJsonRpc\n传输层" as ST #E8F5E9
participant "HTTP客户端" as HC #FFF3E0
participant "HttpJsonRpcServer\n传输层" as HT #FFF3E0
participant "JsonRpc\n核心处理器" as Core #E3F2FD
participant "业务方法" as Business #F3E5F5

== Stdio 传输模式 ==

SC -> ST : 写入stdin\nContent-Length: xxx\n\n{json}
activate ST

note right of ST
  <b>StdioJsonRpc 处理</b>
  1. 异步读取线程
  2. 解析 Content-Length
  3. 读取完整消息体
  4. 验证 JSON 格式
end note

ST -> Core : handleRequest(jsonStr)
activate Core

note right of Core
  <b>核心处理流程</b>
  1. 反序列化 JSON
  2. 验证请求格式
  3. 查找注册方法
  4. 参数验证
end note

Core -> Business : invoke(method, params)
activate Business
Business --> Core : 返回结果
deactivate Business

Core --> ST : 返回响应 JSON
deactivate Core

note right of ST
  <b>响应格式</b>
  Content-Length: xxx\n\n
  { "jsonrpc": "2.0",\n    "result": ..., \n    "id": xxx }
end note

ST -> SC : 写入stdout\nContent-Length: xxx\n\n{json}
deactivate ST

== 批量请求 (Batch) ==

SC -> ST : 批量请求\n[{req1}, {req2}, ...]
ST -> Core : handleBatchRequest()
activate Core

note right of Core
  <b>批量处理</b>
  遍历每个请求
  并行或串行处理
  收集所有响应
end note

loop 每个请求
    Core -> Business : invoke()
    Business --> Core : result
end

Core --> ST : 批量响应\n[{res1}, {res2}, ...]
deactivate Core
ST --> SC : 批量响应

== 通知 (Notification - 无响应) ==

SC -> ST : 通知消息\n{"method":"event","params":...}
ST -> Core : handleRequest(notification)
activate Core

note right of Core
  <b>通知处理</b>
  无 id 字段
  不返回响应
  异步处理
end note

Core -> Business : handleEvent()
deactivate Core

note right of SC
  <b>不等待响应</b>\n客户端立即继续
end note

== HTTP 传输模式 ==

HC -> HT : POST /rpc\nContent-Type: application/json\n{json}
activate HT

note right of HT
  <b>HTTP 处理</b>
  1. 接收 HTTP 请求
  2. 解析 JSON body
  3. 线程池分配
  4. 调用 JSON-RPC 处理
end note

HT -> Core : handleRequest(jsonStr)
activate Core
Core -> Business : invoke(method, params)
activate Business
Business --> Core : 返回结果
deactivate Business
Core --> HT : 返回响应 JSON
deactivate Core

HT --> HC : HTTP 200 OK\nContent-Type: application/json\n{json}
deactivate HT

== SSE 服务端推送 ==

HC -> HT : GET /events\nAccept: text/event-stream
activate HT

note right of HT
  <b>SSE 连接建立</b>
  1. 注册端点
  2. 分配 clientId
  3. 保持长连接
  4. 心跳检测
end note

HT --> HC : HTTP 200 OK\nContent-Type: text/event-stream

== SSE 连接保持活跃 ==

Business -> HT : 需要推送事件
HT -> HC : data: {json}\n\n

note left of HT
  <b>SSE 事件格式</b>
  data: {事件数据}\n\n
  event: 事件类型\n\n
  id: 事件ID\n\n
  retry: 重连时间
end note

deactivate HT

== 错误处理 ==

HC -> HT : POST /rpc\n{无效请求}
HT -> Core : handleRequest(invalid)
activate Core

note right of Core
  <b>错误响应</b>
  Parse Error: -32700
  Invalid Request: -32600
  Method Not Found: -32601
  Invalid Params: -32602
  Internal Error: -32603
end note

Core --> HT : 错误响应\n{"jsonrpc":"2.0","error":{...},"id":null}
deactivate Core

HT --> HC : HTTP 200 OK\n{错误响应}
deactivate HT

note left of Core
  <b>异常情况</b>
  JSON 解析失败\n方法未注册\n参数验证失败\n方法执行异常
end note

legend right
  |= 颜色 |= 含义 |
  | <back:#E8F5E9> Stdio | 标准输入输出传输 |
  | <back:#FFF3E0> HTTP | HTTP/SSE 传输 |
  | <back:#E3F2FD> Core | JSON-RPC 核心处理 |
  | <back:#F3E5F5> 业务 | 业务逻辑方法 |

  <b>关键特性</b>
  • Stdio: 异步读取、LSP格式、批量支持
  • HTTP: 线程池、SSE推送、CORS支持
  • Core: 方法注册、批量请求、通知处理
endlegend

@enduml
